624
00:36:06,200 --> 00:36:08,400
-Let me help you.
-No, thank you.

625
00:36:25,760 --> 00:36:27,440
I saw you in the office

626
00:36:27,520 --> 00:36:29,800
when I handed in homework earlier today.

627
00:36:29,880 --> 00:36:31,000
Were you and Mr. Lin talking

628
00:36:31,080 --> 00:36:32,920
about the academic competition?

629
00:36:36,240 --> 00:36:37,160
No.

630
00:36:40,680 --> 00:36:41,560
<i>Before you transfer,</i>

631
00:36:41,640 --> 00:36:43,520
you need to fill out this application.

632
00:36:43,600 --> 00:36:44,800
Fill this out.

633
00:36:44,880 --> 00:36:47,160
As for the rest of the procedures,
your mom will handle it.

634
00:36:47,240 --> 00:36:48,120
By the way,

635
00:36:48,600 --> 00:36:50,200
there are a few months left.

636
00:36:50,280 --> 00:36:51,760
{\an8}Have you told Gu Ran and others?

637
00:36:53,240 --> 00:36:54,400
Not yet.

638
00:36:54,480 --> 00:36:55,840
You should tell them soon.

639
00:36:56,360 --> 00:36:58,160
Give them time to process it.

640
00:36:58,240 --> 00:36:59,320
