641
00:36:59,400 --> 00:37:01,560
Whenever I'm down,

642
00:37:01,640 --> 00:37:03,600
food can always cheer me up.

643
00:37:03,680 --> 00:37:04,880
Guan Fang said

644
00:37:04,960 --> 00:37:07,760
his grandma recently made a tasty dish.

645
00:37:07,840 --> 00:37:09,000
Su Zaizai, be quiet.

646
00:37:16,080 --> 00:37:16,960
I'm sorry.

647
00:37:17,520 --> 00:37:18,400
I...

648
00:37:18,480 --> 00:37:20,000
You've arrived home. I'll get going.

649
00:37:35,480 --> 00:37:37,480
