650
00:37:41,160 --> 00:37:42,000
Let me help you.

651
00:37:42,080 --> 00:37:43,280
No, thank you.

652
00:37:44,240 --> 00:37:46,200
Su Zaizai, be quiet.

653
00:37:47,000 --> 00:37:48,480
