00:37:53,800 --> 00:37:54,760
EXCLUSIVELY FOR RANGRANG

658
00:37:55,880 --> 00:37:57,320
<i>I bet he must be annoyed.</i>

659
00:38:12,720 --> 00:38:13,920
I'm done eating. I'm leaving.

660
00:38:43,720 --> 00:38:45,120
<i>I will be happy.</i>

661
00:39:23,280 --> 00:39:24,320
Crap.

662
00:39:24,400 --> 00:39:26,400
I'm not happy.

663
00:39:30,040 --> 00:39:33,640
<i>Not even jellies can make me feel better.</i>

664
00:39:34,120 --> 00:39:36,320
<i>I must be beyond saving.</i>
